OL,3,C'The UK is actively participating in
OL,4,Caggression', says senior Iranian
OL,5,Cofficial
OL,7,FInternational Editor Emma Murphy spoke
OL,8,Fwith Dr Saeed Khatibzadeh shortly
OL,9,Fafter Keir Starmer announced British
OL,10,Fbases could be used by Americans to
OL,11,Fattack Iran
OL,13,FIran's deputy foreign secretary has
OL,14,Ftoday warned the United Kingdom will
OL,15,Fbe deemed an aggressor in the war
OL,16,Fagainst Iran and risks repeating the
OL,17,Fmistakes of the Iraq war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
