OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772532302
OL,3,C'The UK is actively participating in
OL,4,Caggression', says senior Iranian
OL,5,Cofficial
OL,7,FI spoke with Dr Saeed Khatibzadeh, on
OL,8,Fthe third day of this war and shortly
OL,9,Fafter Prime Minister Keir Starmer
OL,10,Fannounced British bases could be used
OL,11,Fby the Americans to attack Iran.
OL,13,FHe told me, "What the prime minister
OL,14,Fof UK said yesterday, was actually
OL,15,Factively participating in this
OL,16,Faggression.
OL,18,F"It doesn't matter if are naming it or
OL,19,Fcovering it up by being defensive."
OL,26,@uD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
