OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772532302
OL,3,C'The UK is actively participating in
OL,4,Caggression', says senior Iranian
OL,5,Cofficial
OL,7,FHe likened the decision to someone who
OL,8,Fwas in a gang, robbing a house but
OL,9,Fclaiming they had not been part of the
OL,10,F"dirty" part of the job.
OL,12,F"The people of UK should know that
OL,13,Funfortunately, you are repeating the
OL,14,Fmistake that they did in Iraq, in
OL,15,Ftheir names, and nobody can cover it
OL,16,Fup by calling or coining a new concept
OL,17,Fthat it is defensive."
OL,19,FHe said that anyone working with the
OL,20,FUnited States or Israel was siding
OL,21,Fwith the aggressor.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@GO]tD@AOUyD@VO]
