PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772532302
OL,3,C'The UK is actively participating in
OL,4,Caggression', says senior Iranian
OL,5,Cofficial
OL,7,F"We have no option just to win this
OL,8,Fexistential battle," he said. "I think
OL,9,Fthat the message right now is that, is
OL,10,Fthat people in the UK should ask their
OL,11,Fgovernment to stop actively being
OL,12,Fengaged in this military, illegal,
OL,13,Freckless, unlawful military campaign
OL,14,Fagainst the sovereign state of Iran."
