OL,3,C'The UK is actively participating in
OL,4,Caggression', says senior Iranian
OL,5,Cofficial
OL,7,FRegarding President Trump's claims
OL,8,Fthat Iran was willing to talk and he
OL,9,Fwas willing to talk to them, Dr
OL,10,FKhatibzadeh said, "No country on Earth
OL,11,Fwould talk under aggression and under
OL,12,Fattack.
OL,14,F"He can stop the atrocities, can stop
OL,15,Fattacking, can stop this aggression,
OL,16,Fthen I think that we can see if he is
OL,17,Fgenuinely believes in negotiation,
OL,18,Fdiplomacy and talks."
OL,26,@rD@SOUzD@UO]
