OL,3,C'The UK is actively participating in
OL,4,Caggression', says senior Iranian
OL,5,Cofficial
OL,7,FThe deputy foreign secretary said
OL,8,Fthere was now multi-layered mistrust
OL,9,Fgiven that twice during previous talks
OL,10,Fin June and again last week the US
OL,11,Foffered diplomacy only to launch a war
OL,12,Fmidway through.
OL,14,FHe denied American claims that Iran
OL,15,Fwas seeking a nuclear weapon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
