OL,3,C'The UK is actively participating in
OL,4,Caggression', says senior Iranian
OL,5,Cofficial
OL,7,FHe said: "Please do not buy these
OL,8,Fphoney and fabricated arguments and
OL,9,Fthat the war started because they
OL,10,Fwanted to prevent it on to acquire,
OL,11,Facquire nuclear weapon because there
OL,12,Fwas no and there is no active nuclear
OL,13,Fprogramme on Iranian soil."
